288\; V^2 = \left|\begin{array}{ccccc}  0 & 1 & 1 & 1 & 1 \\ 1 & 0 & d^2 & d^2 & a^2 \\ 1 & d^2 & 0 & d^2 & b^2 \\ 1 & d^2 & d^2 & 0 & c^2 \\ 1 & a^2 & b^2 & c^2 & 0 \end{array}\right| = d^2 \left( \left( a^2+b^2+c^2+d^2 \right)^2-3\left(a^4+b^4+c^4+d^4\right) \right)
